# SDOX Live Preview вҖ” Full Rebuild Plan

## Goal

Rebuild the `/live-preview` page so that **every SDOX tag** from `docs/tags/0.1.0.json` is rendered with a **unique, semantically correct visual** вҖ” not generic boxes. The design must be consistent (one dark-theme design language) but each tag must be visually distinguishable and functionally appropriate.

---

## Current State & Problems

The current `SdoxRenderer.svelte` has **13 tag handlers** but many tags fall into the generic `{:else}` fallback (dashed border box with `#tagname` label). Missing or generic:

