### [MODIFY] [SdoxRenderer.svelte](file:///e:/Project/ip/scalable-document/sdox-web/src/lib/components/preview/SdoxRenderer.svelte)

Complete rewrite with all 28 tags handled individually. Each tag gets:
- Unique HTML structure matching its semantic purpose
- Dedicated CSS class with distinctive styling
- Consistent color palette from the design system

#### Tag-by-Tag Visual Design

---

##### рҹ“„ Structure Category

**`document`** вҖ” Transparent flex container with vertical gap. No visible chrome.

**`title`** вҖ” Dynamic `<h1>`вҖ“`<h6>` with gradient accent underline on `h1`/`h2`. Uses `svelte:element` for dynamic heading level.

**`paragraph`** вҖ” Clean body text with relaxed line height, secondary text color. Supports inline children.

**`section`** вҖ” Grouped container with subtle left accent border and section title styled as small-caps label.

**`divider`** вҖ” Centered decorative divider: thin horizontal line with a diamond `в—Ҷ` symbol in the middle.

---

##### вңҸпёҸ Text & Semantics Category

**`text`** вҖ” Inline `<span>` with conditional classes for `bold`, `italic`, `underline`, `strikethrough`. Supports `color` and `size` attributes via inline style.

**`quote`** вҖ” Blockquote with:
  - Large decorative open-quote mark `"` (oversized, accent-colored, semi-transparent)
  - Italic body text
  - Author attribution right-aligned with em-dash prefix
  - Left gradient border (cyan вҶ’ teal)
  - Subtle background tint

**`note`** вҖ” Callout box with 4 distinct variants:
  - `info` вҖ” Blue left border, `в„№пёҸ` icon, blue tint background
  - `warning` вҖ” Amber left border, `вҡ пёҸ` icon, amber tint background
  - `danger` вҖ” Red left border, `рҹӣ‘` icon, red tint background
  - `success` вҖ” Green left border, `вң…` icon, green tint background
  - Each has a type label pill in the header

---

##### рҹ“Ӣ Lists Category

**`list`** вҖ” Three distinct visual modes:
  - `unordered` вҖ” Custom bullet markers (small cyan dots)
  - `ordered` вҖ” Counter-based numbering with accent-colored numbers
  - `checklist` вҖ” Custom checkbox styling (rounded checkbox with check mark, green when done, strikethrough text when done)

**`item`** вҖ” List item with proper alignment. `done` attribute triggers visual completion state.

---

##### рҹ”— Links & Media Category

**`url`** вҖ” Inline link with accent color, underline on hover, and small external-link SVG icon appended.

**`image`** вҖ” `<figure>` with:
  - Rounded frame with subtle border
  - Hover zoom effect (slight scale)
  - `<figcaption>` from `alt` attribute displayed below

---

##### рҹ’» Code Category

**`code`** вҖ” Delegates to existing `CodeBlock.svelte` component (already well-styled).

**`output`** вҖ” Terminal-style output block:
