  - Type label (`terminal`, `json`, `text`, `html`)
  - Monospace `<pre>` body with slightly green-tinted text

---

##### рҹ“Ҡ Tables Category

**`table`** вҖ” Responsive wrapper with horizontal scroll, rounded corners, border.

**`row`** вҖ” Table row with hover highlight effect and alternating subtle background.

**`cell`** вҖ” Standard cell with padding. Header cells (`header=true`) get:
  - Bold text
  - Darker background
  - Uppercase small-caps styling
  - Accent bottom border

