##### рҹӨ– AI-Native Category

All AI tags share a consistent "AI block" structure but each has a **unique accent color and icon**:

| Tag | Icon | Color | Description |
|-----|------|-------|-------------|
| `metadata` | рҹ“Ӣ | Slate `#94a3b8` | Key-value grid layout |
| `dataset` | рҹ“Ҡ | Purple `#a78bfa` | Named dataset container |
| `example` | рҹ’Ў | Amber `#fbbf24` | Code example with language badge |
| `instruction` | рҹ“қ | Rose `#fb7185` | Instruction with priority badge |
| `response` | рҹӨ– | Emerald `#34d399` | AI response with model badge |
| `embedding` | рҹ§¬ | Teal `#2dd4bf` | Compact embed marker |
| `chunk` | рҹ§© | Orange `#fb923c` | Chunk size container |
| `context` | рҹҺҜ | Sky `#38bdf8` | Context scope container |
| `completion` | вңЁ | Pink `#f472b6` | Completion placeholder |

**AI Block structure:**
```
в”Ңв”Җ ai-header в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ
в”Ӯ [icon] [Label]          [badge(s)]  в”Ӯ
в”ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Ө
в”Ӯ ai-body (children or content)       в”Ӯ
в””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ
```
- Left colored accent border using `--ai-color` CSS variable
- Semi-transparent tinted background
- Badges for attributes (`priority`, `model`, `name`, `scope`, `size`)

**`metadata`** is special вҖ” renders children as a **2-column key-value grid** instead of prose.

**`instruction`** has a **priority badge** with color coding: `high` = red, `medium` = amber, `low` = blue.

